comment: Johnson (BKN) and Brown (BKN) make incidental contact that does not affect DeRozan's (TOR) RSBQ at the start of his drive.
LATR shows Johnson (BKN) legally contests DeRozan's (TOR) shot attempt.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that Williams (BKN) touched the ball last was upheld and TOR is awarded possession.
Lopez (BKN) makes incidental contact and does not affect DeRozan's (TOR) RSBQ at the start of his drive.
Johnson (BKN) and DeRozan (TOR) make incidental contact on the perimeter away from the ball.
L-SLA shows that Vasquez (TOR) has his hand on Williams' (BKN) hip but there is no push that affects his shot attempt.
Patterson (TOR) attempts a take foul on Young (BKN) but never makes contact.
DeRozan (TOR) commits a clear path foul on Johnson (BKN).
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that DeRozan (TOR) committed a clear path foul was upheld.
Johnson (TOR) commits a take foul on Johnson (BKN).
